1507701-a.title: Tenth Avenue - 57th Street looking south

710576f-a.text:
Tenth Ave., east side, south from West 58th (left) to 57th (right) Streets as viewed southeastward across an empty lot at the S.W. corner
of the Ave. and 58th Street.
November 25, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
